text: Kaya tumacyapaiki koni ase icchito ki tyacyajavala khajuricya ani draksancya baga asavyata, jyata panyace pravaha vahata asaveta ani pratyeka prakaraci phale asavita ani bageca malaka mhatara jhalela asava, tyala lahana mulehi asavita ani acanaka tya bagevara agice joradara vadala yave ani ti jaluna khaka vhavi. Asa prakare sarvasrestha allaha tumhala apalya nisanya spastapane sangato, yasathi ki tumhi vicara karava
